      "description": "Edit text in files using literal search-and-replace. All non-no-op edits in a single call succeed atomically or none are applied. Edits with identical old_text and new_text are skipped.\n\nGuidance:\n- Always Read the file first before editing.\n- old_text must match exactly once in the file. Include 3+ surrounding lines for uniqueness.\n- For multi-line matches, preserve exact whitespace and indentation.\n- Special characters in JSON (backticks, quotes, backslashes) must be escaped.\n- Do not issue multiple Edit calls for the same file in one turn — re-read first.\n",
